1. Class Tank -> Implements WeaponUse
    Variables:-
    1.1 Health
    1.2 Fuel
    1.3 Weapons
    Methods:-
    1.4 Move()
    1.5 Shoot() // UseWeapon() from Interface
    1.6 Aim()
    1.7 ChangeWeapon()
    1.8 ReloadWeapons() // AddWeapon() from Interface
    1.9 Remove() // RemoveWeapon() from Interface

2. Class Abrams -> Extending Tank
    Variables:-
    2.1 Health - X;
    2.2 Fuel - X;
    2.3 Weapons - ArrayList of Weapons:-
         2.3.1 Vertical Slam = new Weapon()
         2.3.2 Splitter Chain = new Weapon()
         2.3.3 Big One = new Weapon()
         2.3.4 Air Strike = new Weapon()
         2.3.5 Shotgun = new Weapon()
         2.3.6 Volley = new Weapon()

