5. Class MainMenu
    Methods:-
    5.1 StartGame() = new StartGame()
    5.2 LoadGame() = new LoadGame()
    5.3 Options() = new MainMenuOptions()
    5.4 ExitGame = new ExitGame()

6. Class StartGame -> Extending ChooseTank
    Methods:-
    6.1 StartGame()

7. Class ChooseTank
    Variables-
    7.1 AllTanks = ArrayList of Tanks:-
        7.1.1 Abrams = new Tank()
        7.1.2 Frost = new Tank()
        7.1.3 Spectre = new Tank()
    Methods:-
    7.2 ChooseTank()

